=King |first2=Hans |last2=Sch\u00f6ggl |first3=Karel |last3=Stokkermans |lastauthoramp=y |publisher=RSSSF |date=20 March 2014 |accessdate=29 October 2014}} Select link to season required from chronological list.</ref>\n!rowspan=2|[[Thai FA Cup|FA Cup]]\n!rowspan=2|[[Thai League Cup|League<br /> Cup]]\n!rowspan=2|[[Thailand Champions Cup|Thailand<br /> Champions<br /> Cup]]\n!rowspan=2|[[AFC Champions League|AFC<br /> Champions<br /> League]]\n!colspan=2|Top scorer\n|-\n!Division\n!P\n!W\n!D\n!L\n!F\n!A\n!Pts\n!Pos\n!Name\n!Goals\n|-\n!rowspan=2|2009\n|[[Thai Division 2 League Northern Region 2009|DIV 2 Northern]]\n|20\n|17\n|3\n|0\n|62\n|16\n|54\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|rowspan=2|&nbsp;\u2013\n|rowspan=2|&nbsp;\u2013\n|rowspan=2|&nbsp;\u2013\n|rowspan=2|&nbsp;\u2013\n|rowspan=2|[[Watcharakorn Klaitin]]\n|rowspan=2|19\n|-\n|bgcolor=\"#DDFFDD\"|[[2009 Regional League Division 2|RL]]\n|8\n|3\n|3\n|2\n|12\n|11\n|12\n|bgcolor=silver|2nd\n|-\n!2010\n|bgcolor=\"#DDFFDD\"|[[2010 Thai Division 1 League|DIV 1]]\n|30\n|15\n|8\n|7\n|44\n|32\n|53\n|bgcolor=#deb678|3rd\n|[[2010 Thai FA Cup|R3]]\n|[[2010 Thai League Cup|R2]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Wasan Natasan]]\n|13\n|-\n!2011\n|[[2011 Thai Premier League|TPL]]\n|34\n|11\n|11\n|12\n|47\n|52\n|44\n|10th\n|[[2011 Thai FA Cup|R4]]\n|[[2011 Thai League Cup|QF]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Wasan Natasan]]\n|18\n|-\n!2012\n|[[2012 Thai Premier League|TPL]]\n|34\n|11\n|11\n|12\n|40\n|47\n|44\n|9th\n|[[2012 Thai FA Cup|SF]]\n|[[2012 Thai League Cup|R3]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Nantawat Tansopa]]\n|8\n|-\n!2013\n|[[2013 Thai Premier League|TPL]]\n|32\n|8\n|10\n|14\n|32\n|45\n|34\n|11th\n|[[2013 Thai FA Cup|QF]]\n|[[2013 Thai League Cup|R3]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Leandro Assump\u00e7\u00e3o]]\n|9\n|-\n!2014\n|[[2014 Thai Premier League|TPL]]\n|38\n|13\n|16\n|9\n|55\n|47\n|55\n|7th\n|[[2014 Thai FA Cup|SF]]\n|[[2014 Thai League Cup|R4]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Renan Marques]]\n|17\n|-\n!2015\n|[[2015 Thai Premier League|TPL]]\n|34\n|12\n|8\n|14\n|42\n|57\n|44\n|9th\n|[[2015 Thai FA Cup|QF]]\n|[[2015 Thai League Cup|R1]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Renan Marques]]\n|10\n|-\n!2016\n|[[2016 Thai Premier League|TL]]\n|31\n|13\n|6\n|12\n|42\n|43\n|45\n|8th\n|[[2016 Thai FA Cup|R3]]\n|[[2016 Thai League Cup|R2]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Wellington Bruno]]\n|10\n|-\n!2017\n|[[2017 Thai League|T1]]\n|34\n|18\n|6\n|10\n|67\n|42\n|60\n|4th\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2017 Thai FA Cup|W]]\n|bgcolor=silver|[[2017 Thai League Cup|RU]]\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|&nbsp;\u2013\n|[[Felipe Azevedo]]\n|18\n|-\n!2018\n|[[2018 Thai League|T1]]\n|34\n|15\n|10\n|9\n|52\n|36\n|55\n|5th\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018 Thai FA Cup|W]]\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018 Thai League Cup|W]]\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018 Thailand Champions Cup|W]]\n|[[2018 AFC Champions League|PO]]\n|[[Bill (footballer)|Bill]]\n|9\n|-\n!2019\n|[[2019 Thai League 1|T1]]\n|30\n|16\n|10\n|4\n|53\n|28\n|58\n|bgcolor=gold|1st\n|[[2019 Thai FA Cup|QF]]\n|[[2019 Thai League Cup|SF]]\n|bgcolor=silver|[[2017 Thailand Champions Cup|RU]]\n|[[2019 AFC Champions League|PO]]\n|[[Bill (footballer)|Bill]]\n|14\n|-\n!2020\n|[[2020 Thai League 1|T1]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2020 Thailand Champions Cup|W]]\n|[[2020 AFC Champions League|GS]]\n|\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|bgcolor=gold|<small>Champions</small>\n|bgcolor=silver|<small>Runners-up</small>\n|bgcolor=#deb678|<small>Third place</small>\n|bgcolor=\"#DDFFDD\"|<small>[[Promotion and relegation|Promoted]]</small>\n|bgcolor=\"#FFCCCC\"|<small>[[Promotion and relegation|Relegated]]</small>\n|}\n\n{{Col-begin}}\n{{Col-4}}\n*P = Played\n*W = Games won\n*D = Games drawn\n*L = Games lost\n*F = Goals for\n*A = Goals against\n*Pts = Points\n*Pos = Final position\n*N/A = No answer\n{{Col-4}}\n*TL = [[Thai League 1]]\n{{Col-4}}\n*QR1 = First Qualifying Round\n*QR2 = Second Qualifying Round\n*QR3 = Third Quali